    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. While it still runs, the engine exhibits a noticeable knock and the transmission has begun to slip during shifts. The exterior shows substantial wear, including several large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears and the air conditioning is currently non-functional. This car is being sold as-is and is best suited as a major project or a source for parts.",
